==Description==
The Festival took place on 19th to 21st October 2017, on two sites in Brussels:
* a workshop known as "La Serre" at 171 Rue Gray, Ixelles
* a space called [https://edgeryders.eu/t/au-quai-the-new-festival-venue-for-the-day-2-and-3-and-other-news/7338 Au Quay]

It was announced that Au Quay will close, to be redeveloped, in the coming year.

